==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Divided
<hw>Di*vid"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Parted; disunited;
distributed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Cut into distinct parts, by
incisions which reach the midrib; -- said of a leaf.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dividedly</ent>⟦br⟧
